articles.title: New Jersey governor pleads with Covid-fatigued residents to choose inconvenience over death
articles.description: New Jersey Gov. Phil Murphy tells his constituents tired of Covid-19 restrictions: "You know what's really uncomfortable and annoying? When you die."
articles.content:
